#1 Les fichiers utilisent le charset UFT-8
	Sous Eclipse Window > Preferences > General > Workspace > UTF - 8
	
#2 Le dossier Modules doit  être configuré comme un dossier source
	clic-droit sur PACT > properties > Java build Path > Add folder > tick sur Modules

#3 For Lwjgl, you must pick the OS-relevant natives
	clic-droit sur PACT > Java build path > librairies > expand lwjgl > select natives libs from workspace (/lib/lwjgl/natives/[OS])
	(Note : this can also be achieved by adding the corresponding natives.jar - Just make only one the right one is active at a time)